description.narrative: To assist the Government of Serbia in reducing cost and improving safety for road users through: (a) improving the condition of selected road sections of the main and regional road network; (b) improving the effectiveness of road maintenance through the introduction of performance-based contracting in two pilot regions; and (c) introducing safe road design principles, road safety audits and targeted improvement measures.
